{"tid":581371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【多謝主人】雞姦14 歲男生 戀童積犯囚8年半","createTime":"2018-03-05T09:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T12:11:54.000Z","uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2b246d0f13071c79bdd9351132e2afa5c36c9949","tid":581371,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"曾與網上結識的男童肛交而被判監、有孌童癖的男子，出獄後重施故技，於前年<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逼一名於網上同性戀討論區認識的14歲男生為他口交並雞姦對方，又與他大玩「主人與奴隸」性虐待，拍打男生陽具及臀部後要對方回應「多謝主人」，將過程拍下。</span></span>孌童癖男子早前承認非禮及肛交等7罪，法官今判刑指心理專家評估被告重犯機會高，對公眾構成危害，被告又用威迫手段令事主就範，需要加判，最終判他入獄8年6個月。<br />\n<br />\n報稱任職司機的積犯羅俊彥（30歲）早前承認非禮、向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為、肛交、製作兒童色情物品共七罪。辯方今進一步求情，指被告有家人、教會及朋友支持，他們會支持重新做人，被告亦承諾會接受治療。法官判刑時指，被告過往有4次案底，2016年因肛交罪被判入獄28個月，出獄不久便再犯，兩名心理醫生評估被告有反社會人格，而被告過往拒絕接受治療，故被告重犯機會甚高，對社會構成潛在危險。<br />\n<br />\n法官又指被告假扮成「弟弟」與「結拜兄弟」，威脅事主若不肯就範就危及他的家人；被告又在事主要求終止關係後將性愛影片透過facebook向事主的朋友發布，對事主造成重大壓力。雖然事主最終似乎未留下重大創傷，但被告種種行為屬加刑因素。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520228761_bc68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520228761_bc68.jpg&h=64a0160d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告羅俊彥（蒙頭者）(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180305&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57906656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180305%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57906656&d=mR%2Fc%2Bzps6cEDNrZ8EtMDxXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=27eaac83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180305%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57906656&h=2c476b6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180305&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57906656</a><br />\n<br />\n正人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友一定好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e74a0cb9974ab0b75384e560a81542d3bb5a44","tid":581371,"uid":24160,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://images3.imagebam.com/46/61/16/5394c3358431320.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages3.imagebam.com%2F46%2F61%2F16%2F5394c3358431320.jpg&d=mR%2Fc%2Bzps6cEDNrZ8EtMDxXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=af770f40\" target=\"_blank\">http://images3.imagebam.com/46/61/16/5394c3358431320.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94019a0fbef9f373249c64eb8725bb89b36636fc","tid":581371,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb733729247e86f2d15729109d87e87c14f76d6","tid":581371,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"網上同性戀討論區認識的14歲男生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d726de9e5c911be4ec806c0b84b84c7b5effa3a3","tid":581371,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:03:13.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"86fc0a42b7881a76d5e8c7c88cd367fab976bb7f","tid":581371,"uid":17368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"多謝主主人"},{"pid":"6976552b5666c0151678204bdbc98f1104670c0f","tid":581371,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86fc0a42b7881a76d5e8c7c88cd367fab976bb7f","tid":5813